SUMMARY:Opening Day at Oaks Amusement Park
DESCRIPTION:Head to Oaks Amusement Park on March 21 as they kick off our 121st season with rides\, mini golf\, carnival games\, and roller skating. They’ll be open every day of Oregon Spring Break\, then weekends throughout the spring.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/opening-day-at-oaks-amusement-park/
LOCATION:Oaks Amusement Park\, 7805 SE Oaks Park Way\, Portland\, OR\, 97202
CATEGORIES:Active,Family Fun,Kids Calendar
