SUMMARY:TITANIC: The Artifact Exhibition at OMSI
DESCRIPTION:TITANIC: The Artifact Exhibition | March 21\, 2026 to October 18\, 2026 \nHistory comes to life in TITANIC: The Artifact Exhibition. This immersive exhibition offers a rare opportunity for audiences of all ages to explore the innovation\, ambition\, and tragedy of Titanic while connecting personally with the people whose lives were forever changed by her voyage. Step back to April 1912 and assume the role of a passenger on the Ship’s first and final journey. With more than 100 authentic artifacts recovered from the wrecksite\, guests are immersed in life aboard Titanic and the deeply human stories behind one of history’s most enduring legends. \nBe sure to confirm hours on OMSI’s website! \nPlease note: Timed entrance allows guests to join the exhibit queue at their selected time. Please allow time for both queuing and the exhibit experience. Last entry to the exhibit will be one hour before closing time. \nDiscounted admission of $6 per person for OMSI Members. Children 2 and under visit for free. Member discounts are applied at checkout.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/titanic-the-artifact-exhibition-at-omsi/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:OMSI
CATEGORIES:Educational,Indoor,Kids Calendar,Museum
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/titanic-at-omsi.jpg
END:VEVENT
