SUMMARY:Junior Symphony of Vancouver Spring Concert
DESCRIPTION:The Junior Symphony of Vancouver Spring Concert program will include music by Modest Mussorgsky\, Ralph Vaughan-Williams\, and Bela Bartok.  This concert will also feature long-time JSV participant Brian Anderson performing the 1st movement of Mozart’s Violin Concerto #5! \nTickets $15 general – available at the door. Reception follows.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/junior-symphony-of-vancouver-spring-concert/
LOCATION:Cascades Presbyterian Church\, 9503 NE 86th Street\, Vancouver\, WA
CATEGORIES:Indoor,Kids Calendar,Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/junior-symphony-orchestra.jpg
END:VEVENT
