SUMMARY:Bunny’s Breakfast Bash at Dave & Buster's
DESCRIPTION:Spring into fun with a playful morning at Dave & Buster’s Clackamas!\nEnjoy exclusive early access to the arcade\, a banquet-style breakfast\, spring activities\, and festive photo opportunities with the Bunny himself. \nKids can join our Arcade Egg Hunt at 9:45 am\, featuring fun prizes—including the chance to ride the Human Crane! \nChoose Your Family’s Fun:\nEggstra Fun Ticket: Banquet style breakfast with soda\, coffee\, tea\, & assorted juices\, a $10 Power Card with Unlimited Video Game Play during the event\, egg hunt\, crafting\, and Bunny photos. \nBrekky Basket Ticket: Banquet style breakfast with soda\, coffee\, tea\, & assorted juices. \nTickets must be purchased online before the event. \nDon’t miss this egg-citing morning of food\, fun\, and family memories. We can’t wait to celebrate with you! \nThis event is over $30. We only include links for higher-priced events from our advertisers — but it’s easy to find with a quick search! \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/bunnys-breakfast-bash-at-dave-busters/
LOCATION:Dave and Buster’s – Clackamas\, 11860 SE 82nd Ave\, Happy Valley\, OR\, 97086\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts/Crafts,Easter,Family Fun,Gaming,Indoor,Kids Calendar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/easter-generic.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Dave &amp%3B Buster's":MAILTO:Tammy.gotti@daveandbusters.com
END:VEVENT
