SUMMARY:Bunny Cares - A Sensory-Friendly Event
DESCRIPTION:This event is thoughtfully designed to accommodate sensory sensitivities by reducing crowds\, adjusting lighting and lowering music volume.  Families can reserve timeslots online to ensure minimal wait times\, and Bunny\, along with staff\, received specialized training to offer a supportive and welcoming experience for guests with sensory needs. Guests of all abilities are encouraged to attend.  While the visit is free\, photo packages will be available for purchase. \nThis event is in partnership with Autism Speaks\, and is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/bunny-cares-a-sensory-friendly-event/
LOCATION:Washington Square Mall\, 9585 SW Washington Square Rd\, Portland\, OR. 97223\, Portland\, OR\, 97223\, United States
CATEGORIES:Easter,Family Fun,Inclusive,Indoor,Kids Calendar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Easter-Generic-1.jpg
